                <div class="comment-text">
                    <p>You don&#8217;t get it. It IS backed by something. BTC is backed by an algorithm. That&#8217;s the entire point. Why is the algorithm good? </p>
<p>1. You can&#8217;t steal it.<br />
2. You can&#8217;t change it.<br />
3. You can&#8217;t transfer it to someone else.<br />
4. You can&#8217;t re-hypothecate it.<br />
5. You can&#8217;t fake it.<br />
6. You can&#8217;t duplicate it.<br />
7. You can&#8217;t use paperwork to screw it up. </p>
<p>It&#8217;s better backing than anything else out there.  There is no stopping the crypto-currency movement. It will transform the financial structure of this world.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rtp-reply rtp-common-link"><a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2014/03/21/what-is-payment-protocol-ripple-and-how-does-it-allow-for-physically-backed-digital-gold-trading/?replytocom=22295#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-22295", "22295", "respond", "11524")'>Reply</a></div>

