                    <span class="comment-meta">
                        <a class="rtp-common-link rtp-comment-date" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/03/21/what-is-payment-protocol-ripple-and-how-does-it-allow-for-physically-backed-digital-gold-trading/#comment-22307" title="March 22, 2014">
